---
const APP_URL = "https://accounting-bridge.streamlit.app"
---

<section id="pricing" class="py-20 sm:py-28">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
    <div class="text-center mb-4 fade-in-up">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-dark mb-4">Pricing</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-muted max-w-xl mx-auto">
        30-day free trial on all plans. No implementation cost. No IT. Cancel anytime.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 lg:gap-6 mt-16">
      <!-- Starter -->
      <div class="fade-in-up rounded-2xl p-8 bg-white border border-border shadow-sm flex flex-col">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-dark">Starter</h3>
        <div class="mt-4 mb-2">
          <span class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-dark">$1,500</span>
          <span class="text-muted">/mo</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted mb-8">Save your team 10+ hours every close. Excel in, Excel out.</p>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-muted mb-8 flex-grow">
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-primary">&#x2713;</span> Up to 3 entities</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-primary">&#x2713;</span> 1 user</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-primary">&#x2713;</span> All 4 processing modes</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-primary">&#x2713;</span> AI narrative summaries</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-primary">&#x2713;</span> Email support</li>
        </ul>
        <a href={APP_URL}
           class="block text-center px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-primary border-2 border-primary/20 hover:border-primary/40 rounded-xl transition-colors no-underline">
          Start free trial
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Growth (featured) -->
      <div class="fade-in-up rounded-2xl p-8 bg-white border-2 border-primary shadow-lg shadow-primary/10 flex flex-col relative">
        <div class="absolute -top-3.5 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 px-4 py-1 bg-primary text-white text-xs font-bold rounded-full">
          Most popular
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-dark">Growth</h3>
        <div class="mt-4 mb-2">
          <span class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-dark">$3,000</span>
          <span class="text-muted">/mo</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted mb-8">Stop chasing files across entities. One consolidated TB, audit-ready, every month.</p>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-muted mb-8 flex-grow">
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-primary">&#x2713;</span> Unlimited entities</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-primary">&#x2713;</span> Up to 3 users</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-primary">&#x2713;</span> All 4 processing modes</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-primary">&#x2713;</span> AI narrative summaries</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-primary">&#x2713;</span> Priority support</li>
        </ul>
        <a href={APP_URL}
           class="block text-center px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white bg-primary hover:bg-primary-hover rounded-xl transition-colors no-underline">
          Start free trial
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Enterprise -->
      <div class="fade-in-up rounded-2xl p-8 bg-white border border-border shadow-sm flex flex-col">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-dark">Enterprise</h3>
        <div class="mt-4 mb-2">
          <span class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-dark">Custom</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted mb-8">Roll out across your portfolio. The junior analyst you can't hire, at 1% of the cost.</p>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-muted mb-8 flex-grow">
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-primary">&#x2713;</span> Unlimited entities & users</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-primary">&#x2713;</span> Dedicated onboarding</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-primary">&#x2713;</span> Custom KPI definitions</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-primary">&#x2713;</span> Priority support</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-primary">&#x2713;</span> Vendor security questionnaire</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="mailto:wietze.suijker@gmail.com?subject=Accounting%20Bridge%20Enterprise"
           class="block text-center px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-primary border-2 border-primary/20 hover:border-primary/40 rounded-xl transition-colors no-underline">
          Contact us
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Bottom CTA for finance leaders -->
    <div class="fade-in-up mt-16 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center">
      <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed">
        Your team spends 10-40 hours a month on manual consolidation. At a $75 loaded rate, that's
        $9,000-36,000/year in recoverable labor. No IT project. No implementation fee.
        Cancel if it doesn't deliver in 30 days.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
